Grammar

    0 $accept: function $end

    1 function: function_header variables body

    2 function_header: FUNCTION IDENTIFIER optional_parameters RETURNS type ';'

    3 optional_parameters: parameters
    4                    | %empty

    5 parameters: parameters ',' parameter
    6           | parameter

    7 parameter: IDENTIFIER ':' type

    8 variables: variables variable
    9          | %empty

   10 variable: IDENTIFIER ':' type IS statement_
   11         | IDENTIFIER ':' LIST OF type IS list ';'

   12 type: INTEGER
   13     | REAL
   14     | CHARACTER

   15 list: '(' expressions ')'

   16 expressions: expressions ',' expression
   17            | expression

   18 body: BEGIN_ statement_ END ';'

   19 statement_: statement ';'
   20           | error ';'

   21 statement: expression
   22          | WHEN condition ',' expression ':' expression
   23          | SWITCH expression IS cases OTHERS ARROW statement_ ENDSWITCH
   24          | IF condition THEN statement_ elsif_clauses ELSE statement_ ENDIF
   25          | FOLD direction operator list_choice ENDFOLD

   26 elsif_clauses: elsif_clauses ELSIF condition THEN statement_
   27              | %empty

   28 cases: cases case
   29      | %empty

   30 case: CASE INT_LITERAL ARROW statement_

   31 direction: LEFT
   32          | RIGHT

   33 operator: ADDOP
   34         | MULOP

   35 list_choice: list
   36            | IDENTIFIER

   37 condition: or_condition

   38 or_condition: or_condition OROP and_condition
   39             | and_condition

   40 and_condition: and_condition ANDOP not_condition
   41              | not_condition

   42 not_condition: NOTOP not_condition
   43              | relation

   44 relation: '(' condition ')'
   45         | expression RELOP expression

   46 expression: expression ADDOP term
   47           | term

   48 term: term MULOP power
   49     | term MODOP power
   50     | power

   51 power: unary EXPOP power
   52      | unary

   53 unary: NEGOP unary
   54      | primary

   55 primary: '(' expression ')'
   56        | INT_LITERAL
   57        | REAL_LITERAL
   58        | CHAR_LITERAL
   59        | IDENTIFIER '(' expression ')'
   60        | IDENTIFIER


Terminals, with rules where they appear

    $end (0) 0
    '(' (40) 15 44 55 59
    ')' (41) 15 44 55 59
    ',' (44) 5 16 22
    ':' (58) 7 10 11 22
    ';' (59) 2 11 18 19 20
    error (256) 20
    IDENTIFIER <iden> (258) 2 7 10 11 36 59 60
    INT_LITERAL <type> (259) 30 56
    REAL_LITERAL <type> (260) 57
    CHAR_LITERAL <type> (261) 58
    ADDOP (262) 33 46
    MULOP (263) 34 48
    MODOP (264) 49
    EXPOP (265) 51
    NEGOP (266) 53
    ANDOP (267) 40
    OROP (268) 38
    NOTOP (269) 42
    RELOP (270) 45
    ARROW (271) 23 30
    BEGIN_ (272) 18
    CASE (273) 30
    CHARACTER (274) 14
    ELSE (275) 24
    ELSIF (276) 26
    END (277) 18
    ENDIF (278) 24
    ENDFOLD (279) 25
    ENDSWITCH (280) 23
    FOLD (281) 25
    FUNCTION (282) 2
    IF (283) 24
    INTEGER (284) 12
    IS (285) 10 11 23
    LEFT (286) 31
    LIST (287) 11
    OF (288) 11
    OTHERS (289) 23
    REAL (290) 13
    RETURNS (291) 2
    RIGHT (292) 32
    SWITCH (293) 23
    THEN (294) 24 26
    WHEN (295) 22


Nonterminals, with rules where they appear

    $accept (46)
        on left: 0
    function <type> (47)
        on left: 1
        on right: 0
    function_header (48)
        on left: 2
        on right: 1
    optional_parameters <type> (49)
        on left: 3 4
        on right: 2
    parameters <type> (50)
        on left: 5 6
        on right: 3 5
